title: Blinken, in Indonesia, Stresses Soft Power to Counter China
content:
1. Blinken, in Indonesia, Stresses Soft Power to Counter China  The New York Times
  2. Blinken says the Indo-Pacific will shape the trajectory of the 21st century as counterweight to China's aggressive actions  CNN
  3. Antony Blinken says U.S. to advance alliances in Indo-Pacific region  Reuters
  4. Antony Blinken warns China to stop ‘aggressive actions’ in Asia-Pacific  The Guardian
  5. Blinken warns China to stop 'aggressive actions' in first trip to Southeast Asia  The Washington Post
